        5816
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        5821,
        5895
      ],
      "content": "In the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Cloud service<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> list, perform one of the following sets of steps:"
    },
    {
      "content": "In the dropdown list box, choose an existing cloud service.",
      "pos": [
        5903,
        5962
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The data center location for the service appears.",
      "pos": [
        5963,
        6012
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You should note this location and make sure that your storage account location is in the same data center.",
      "pos": [
        6013,
        6119
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Choose <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Create New<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> to create a cloud service that Azure hosts.",
      "pos": [
        6128,
        6193
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "In the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Create Cloud Service<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> dialog box, provide a name for the service, and then specify a region or affinity group to specify the location of the data center that you want to host this cloud service.",
      "pos": [
        6194,
        6398
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The name must be unique in Azure.",
      "pos": [
        6399,
        6432
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "In the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Environment<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> list, choose either <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Production<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> or <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Staging<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        6437,
        6510
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Choose the staging environment if you want to deploy your application to a test environment.",
      "pos": [
        6511,
        6603
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can move your application to the production environment later.",
      "pos": [
        6604,
        6670
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        6675,
        6751
      ],
      "content": "In the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Build configuration<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> list, choose either <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Debug<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> or <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Release<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept>."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        6756,
        6832
      ],
      "content": "In the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Service configuration<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> list, choose either <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Cloud<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> or <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Local<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept>."
    },
    {
      "content": "Select the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Enable Remote Desktop for all roles<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> check box if you want to be able to remotely connect to the service.",
      "pos": [
        6838,
        6957
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "This option is primarily used for troubleshooting.",
      "pos": [
        6958,
        7008
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "When you select this check box, the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Remote Desktop Configuration<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> dialog box appears.",
      "pos": [
        7009,
        7097
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Choose the Settings link to change the configuration.",
      "pos": [
        7098,
        7151
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Select the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Enable Web Deploy for all web roles<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> check box to enable web deployment for the service.",
      "pos": [
        7157,
        7259
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You must enable Remote Desktop to use this feature.",
      "pos": [
        7260,
        7311
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For more information, see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt>Publishing a Cloud Service using the Azure Tools<ept id=\"p2\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/azure/ff683672.aspx)</ept><ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/azure/ff683672.aspx)</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        7312,
        7503
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For more information about Web Deploy, see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt>Publishing a Cloud Service using the Azure Tools<ept id=\"p2\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/azure/ff683672.aspx)</ept><ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/azure/ff683672.aspx)</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        7504,
        7712
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Choose the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Advanced Settings<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> tab.",
      "pos": [
        7717,
        7754
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "In the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Deployment label<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> field, either accept the default name, or enter a name of your choosing.",
      "pos": [
        7755,
        7855
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "To append the date to the deployment label, leave the check box selected.",
      "pos": [
        7856,
        7929
      ]
